    <briefdescription>
<para>Describes a text fit candidate for candidate-based text fit. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each fit candidate defines a font size and line height configuration that can be selected during text fit.</para>
<para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Text" kindref="compound">Text</ref> fit selects the largest candidate that fits into the available layout space.</para>
<para>The line height is specified as an absolute value.</para>
<para>This object is used to configure candidate-based text fit behavior. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
